 />\n不過我睇法係，有部份淺藍人士唔係真係非撐中不可，而係距離問題。即係 「果啲後生仔搞亂」「網上啲人點點點」。佢地平時接觸既人同媒體同我地都有分別。<br />\n<br />\n但當罷工 <strong>就係你隔離位發生</strong>，就唔同講法"},{"pid":"75dfee26e4b15c7d1ce79127f32ade4635abddc8","tid":1360683,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"無，老實講，九成部門唔運作對市民既影響都唔大"},{"pid":"568a40edcc1152f42d846ea78ef28917e7f34605","tid":1360683,"uid":270544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"善用 CSR 904 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9e84923af4295325da972ca75ff6b0a0ff16bc","tid":1360683,"uid":34577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"568a40edcc1152f42d846ea78ef28917e7f34605","tid":1360683,"uid":270544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"善用 CSR 904 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"善用 SL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb64c8cc36d63c3a05760e3460e9617d128fae0e","tid":1360683,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得一定要攪！驚比人認得就帶口罩、蒙面"},{"pid":"901c2064bb9f3f5975867e25141806e859dc2ea1","tid":1360683,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:46:11.000Z","msg":"叫巴士公司, 小巴, 地鐵 一齊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b00c530b49f9368bfcfe588e9e2570ea5881ba0","tid":1360683,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75dfee26e4b15c7d1ce79127f32ade4635abddc8","tid":1360683,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"無，老實講，九成部門唔運作對市民既影響都唔大"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"一日半日就唔大, 如果幾日,